<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SeatTrace - 도면 정리</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin/seatmap-header.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin/seatmap-workspace.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin/seatmap-crop-rotate.css">
</head>

<body class="seatmap-crop-body">
{{> admin/seatmap/common/header}}
{{> admin/seatmap/common/work-toolbar}}

<main class="crop-page">
    <aside class="crop-side">
        <section class="crop-panel">
            <span class="crop-panel__eyebrow">STEP 01</span>
            <h1>도면 정리</h1>
            <p>원본 PNG를 그대로 띄우고, 마우스로 저장할 영역을 직접 드래그합니다. 선택 영역 안은 원본 그대로 유지되고 바깥 영역만 흐리게 표시됩니다.</p>

            <div class="crop-info">
                <label>현재 도면</label>
                <strong id="cropProjectName">도면 없음</strong>
                <small id="cropProjectPath">새 도면을 먼저 생성하세요.</small>
            </div>

            <div class="crop-actions">
                <button type="button" class="crop-action crop-action--primary" id="applyFullCrop">전체 영역 선택</button>
                <button type="button" class="crop-action" id="clearCropArea">영역 다시 선택</button>
                <button type="button" class="crop-action" id="openMainPage">메인으로</button>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="crop-panel crop-panel--compact">
            <h2>저장 대상</h2>
            <code id="cropSavePath">/temp/seatmap/도면명/seatmap-image.png</code>
        </section>
    </aside>

    <section class="crop-stage">
        <div class="crop-stage__top">
            <strong>미리보기</strong>
            <span>이미지 위를 드래그해서 자를 영역을 선택하세요.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="crop-canvas-wrap" id="cropCanvasWrap">
            <canvas id="cropCanvas"></canvas>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>

<script defer src="/js/admin/seatmap-header.js"></script>
<script defer src="/js/admin/seatmap-crop-rotate.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
